		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Viv&eacute; Griffith</span></strong> lives in Austin, Texas, just five hundred feet from the so-called <span class="smallcaps">NAFTA</span> superhighway. She directs the Free Minds Project, a free humanities course for low-income adults who haven&rsquo;t been to college. &ldquo;My students range in age from twenty-three to fifty-six,&rdquo; she writes, &ldquo;and they discuss Plato with gusto.&rdquo;</p><a href="/contributors/vive-griffith" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
